articles.title: Una Healy reunites with children at home after holiday with David Haye and Sian Osborne - RSVP Live
articles.description: Singer and broadcaster Una Healy spent the Christmas break in London and Morocco while her kids celebrated the festive season with their dad Ben Foden in America
articles.content:
Una Healy has reunited with her two children after spending Christmas apart.
